PN,31801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FThe rollout of the Covid-19 vaccines,
OL,8,Fcoupled with therapeutic programmes,
OL,9,Fwas one of the "success stories of the
OL,10,Fpandemic," according to the chair of
OL,11,Fthe Covid-19 inquiry.
OL,13,FBaroness Heather Hallet delivered the
OL,14,Finquiry's fourth report on Thursday,
OL,15,Fwith a focus on vaccines and
OL,16,Ftherapeutic treatments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FDespite the success of the vaccine
OL,8,Fprogramme, Hallet said there had been
OL,9,Flower uptake among some ethnic
OL,10,Fminority groups and in communities
OL,11,Fsuffering from greater deprivation.
OL,13,FShe found that lack of confidence in
OL,14,Fthe vaccines was a global issue,
OL,15,Fdriven by the spread of false
OL,16,Finformation online and the vaccines'
OL,17,Fquick development.
OL,19,FThe report states that issues of trust
OL,20,Fwere not limited to healthcare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FBroader experiences of racism and
OL,8,Fdiscrimination contributed to vaccine
OL,9,Fhesitancy among some ethnic minority
OL,10,Fcommunities.
OL,12,FPrevious events that particularly
OL,13,Faffected Black people, such as the
OL,14,FWindrush scandal and the Grenfell Fire
OL,15,Ftragedy, created a perception that
OL,16,Fgovernments have not been acting in
OL,17,Ftheir best interests, resulting in a
OL,18,Fhigher reluctance to engage with
OL,19,Fstatutory services.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FIn her report, Hallet makes five
OL,8,Frecommendations to improve the UK's
OL,9,Freadiness for future pandemics.
OL,11,FThese include establishing a new panel
OL,12,Fof experts to oversee vaccine
OL,13,Fdevelopment and rollouts, as well as
OL,14,Fseveral measures aimed at building
OL,15,Ftrust and access to vaccines,
OL,16,Fsomething she says must be undertaken
OL,17,Fin all four nations of the UK before
OL,18,Fany future pandemics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FWriting in her report, Hallet said:
OL,8,F"The vaccination programme was an
OL,9,Fextraordinary feat. Effective vaccines
OL,10,Fwere developed, produced and delivered
OL,11,Fto the majority of the population in
OL,12,Frecord time.
OL,14,F"However, while the majority of people
OL,15,Ftook up the offer of vaccination,
OL,16,Fthere was lower uptake within
OL,17,Fcommunities in areas of higher
OL,18,Fdeprivation and in some ethnic
OL,19,Fminority communities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,F"Governments and health services must
OL,8,Fwork with communities to rebuild trust
OL,9,Fand promote a better understanding of,
OL,10,Fand confidence in, vaccines."
OL,12,FBy June 2021, 95.4% of people in the
OL,13,Fwhite-British group over the age of 50
OL,14,Fwere vaccinated.
OL,16,FBy comparison, uptake was 15% lower
OL,17,Famong white-other, Asian, Asian
OL,18,FBritish-Pakistani, and Chinese ethnic
OL,19,Fgroups.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FUptake was 20% lower among the Black
OL,8,For Black British-African group, and
OL,9,F29% lower among the Black or Black
OL,10,FBritish-Caribbean group.
OL,12,FDespite the successes of the vaccine
OL,13,Fprogramme in the UK, Hallet drew
OL,14,Fattention to the inquiry's assessment
OL,15,Fthat "the UK entered the pandemic
OL,16,Fwithout sufficient manufacturing
OL,17,Fcapability", and that this must be
OL,18,Faddressed before future crises.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FShe also addressed the small number of
OL,8,Fpeople who suffered harm as a result
OL,9,Fof having the vaccine, saying: "This
OL,10,Fwas a small minority compared to the
OL,11,Foverall scale of the vaccination
OL,12,Fprogramme, but of no less importance
OL,13,Fto the individuals affected and their
OL,14,Ffamilies."
OL,16,FAlthough comparatively rare, there
OL,17,Fwere cases of people suffering serious
OL,18,Finjury or death as a result of
OL,19,Fvaccination.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FHallet deemed the current scheme
OL,8,Finadequate, with the report finding
OL,9,Frepresentatives of vaccine-injured and
OL,10,Fbereaved groups felt silenced,
OL,11,Fignored, or treated as vaccine deniers.
OL,13,FPeople injured by the Covid-19 vaccine
OL,14,Fcan apply to the existing Vaccine
OL,15,FDamage Payment Scheme, which was
OL,16,Fintroduced in 1979.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FThose able to establish that
OL,8,Fthemselves or a relative suffered
OL,9,Fsevere disablement of 60% or more and
OL,10,Fthat, on a balance of probabilities,
OL,11,Fthe vaccine caused the injury or death
OL,12,Fcan apply for payment.
OL,14,FThe scheme was expanded in December
OL,15,F2020 to include Covid-19 vaccines.
OL,17,FBy January 2025, there had been 17,519
OL,18,Fapplications to the scheme in respect
OL,19,Fof Covid-19 vaccines.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FThe UK government's rationale for
OL,8,Fadding Covid-19 vaccines to the
OL,9,Fexisting scheme in December 2020
OL,10,Fserved to demonstrate its confidence
OL,11,Fin the safety of them; and to ensure
OL,12,Fthat there was financial provision in
OL,13,Fthe rare cases where any individual
OL,14,Fwas severely disabled as a result of
OL,15,Fvaccination.
OL,17,FBetween 2021 and 2023, 125
OL,18,Fapplications resulted in payment and
OL,19,F2,266 applications were refused.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FThe report urges that payments should
OL,8,Fbe increased and the ease of making a
OL,9,Fclaim be reformed as soon as possible.
OL,11,FAt the outset of the coronavirus
OL,12,Fpandemic, the UK deployed a Vaccine
OL,13,FTask Force, led by Dame Kate Bingham,
OL,14,Fto find the most promising vaccines
OL,15,Fand pre-order them for speedy
OL,16,Fdeployment once approved by regulators.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FIn November 2020, Pfizer/BioNTech
OL,8,Fannounced that its Covid-19 vaccine
OL,9,Fwas both safe and effective, swiftly
OL,10,Ffollowed by a similar announcement
OL,11,Fabout the Moderna jab. Days later the
OL,12,FOxford/AstraZeneca vaccine was also
OL,13,Fannounced to be effective at
OL,14,Fprotecting against disease.
OL,16,FRegulators worked in tandem with
OL,17,Fscientists so the jabs could be
OL,18,Fapproved as quickly as possible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FOn December 8, 2020, grandmother
OL,8,FMargaret Keenan, then 90, became the
OL,9,Ffirst person in the world to be given
OL,10,Fa Covid-19 jab outside of a clinical
OL,11,Ftrial as she received the Pfizer/
OL,12,FBioNTech jab in Coventry.
OL,14,FThe Oxford jab was approved for use on
OL,15,FDecember 30 2020, hailed as a "massive
OL,16,Fstep forward in our fight against
OL,17,Fcoronavirus" by then-Health Secretary
OL,18,FMatt Hancock.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FThe NHS rolled out the vaccines at
OL,8,Fpace, prioritising the most vulnerable
OL,9,Fin society.
OL,11,FThousands of vaccination sites were
OL,12,Fset up across the UK, including in
OL,13,Ffootball stadiums, shopping malls and
OL,14,Fcathedrals.
OL,16,FClinics operated 24 hours a day to get
OL,17,Fpeople vaccinated as quickly as
OL,18,Fpossible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FAccording to NHS data, as of February
OL,8,F1 2026, more than 184 million
OL,9,Fvaccinations have been administered in
OL,10,FEngland.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
