OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,FAlthough the rollout of the Covid-19
OL,8,Fvaccine programme was described in
OL,9,FThursday's report as "an extraordinary
OL,10,Ffeat", Baroness Hallet outlined
OL,11,Fseveral areas needing urgent
OL,12,Fimprovement before any future
OL,13,Fpandemics.
OL,15,FBaroness Hallet said: "We cannot know
OL,16,Fwhen, but there will be another
OL,17,Fpandemic. My recommendations, taken as
OL,18,Fa whole, should mean that the UK is
OL,19,Fbetter prepared for that pandemic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776395018
OL,3,CCovid vaccines 'extraordinary feat',
OL,4,Cbut work needed to improve trust and
OL,5,Caccess
OL,7,F"I urge governments across the UK to
OL,8,Fwork individually and collectively to
OL,9,Fimplement these recommendations, in
OL,10,Ffull and in a timely manner."
OL,12,F43 witnesses gave oral evidence during
OL,13,FModule 4 public hearings held in
OL,14,FLondon in January 2025.
OL,16,FThursday's report is the fourth
OL,17,Fpublished by the Covid-19 inquiry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
